{"title":"czq的子区间和","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1191#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1191","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1191/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1191/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1191"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定一个长度为 $n$ 的数组 $a_i$，统计有多少子区间 $[l,r](l\\leq r)$，满足 $\\displaystyle\\sum_{i=l}^r a_i \\equiv x\\pmod{m}$。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行三个整数 $n,m,x$，由空格隔开。\r\n\r\n接下来第二行有 $n$ 个整数 $a_i$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅一行，为满足条件的子区间的个数。\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n9 9 6\r\n0 3 5 2 5 1 4 0 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n5\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例解释\r\n```\r\n满足条件的区间为：a[0,4],a[0,8],a[1,4],a[1,8],a[4,5]\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq m \\leq 10^9$\r\n\r\n$0 \\leq x,a_i < m$\r\n"}]}